b0\u1eddn th\u00e1nh nh\u01b0ng ai n\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u01b0\u1edfi \u1ea5m l\u1ea1 th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u00e1nh n\u1ebfn nguy\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u tha thi\u1ebft du d\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2ng l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00f2a Thi\u00ean Ch\u00faa cho c\u00e1c b\u1eadc t\u1ed5 ti\u00ean, \u00f4ng b\u00e0, cha m\u1eb9 v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n y\u00eau. M\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c an b\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp trong l\u00f2ng m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi qua l\u1eddi c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed1i h\u00f2a theo ti\u1ebfng h\u00e1t.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/phatdiem.org\/User_folder_upload\/userfiles\/images\/langvan.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u1ede m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c v\u01b0\u1eddn th\u00e1nh nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng d\u1ecdn m\u00ecnh l\u00e3nh nh\u1eadn b\u00ed t\u00edch H\u00f2a gi\u1ea3i, m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1eadt \u00fd ngh\u0129a: ch\u00ednh n\u01a1i \u201cngh\u0129a \u0111\u1ecba\u201d ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c n\u00e0y, qua b\u00ed t\u00edch H\u00f2a gi\u1ea3i, t\u1ed9i nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao h\u00f2a v\u1edbi Ch\u00faa nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee5c sinh t\u00e2m h\u1ed3n.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea5t ch\u1ee3t t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn l\u00ean l\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e0i\u00a0<em>(d\u1ef1ng l\u00ean t\u1eeb h\u00f4m Th\u00e1nh l\u1ec5 ng\u00e0y 02.11)<\/em>\u00a0v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi Th\u00e1nh v\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c treo hai b\u00ean nh\u01b0 c\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed1i:<\/p>\n<p><em>\u201cKh\u00fac ai ca Ch\u00faa \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u<\/em>,<\/p>\n<p>M\u1eb7c cho con l\u1ec5 ph\u1ee5c huy ho\u00e0ng\u201d.(Tv 29,12).<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/phatdiem.org\/User_folder_upload\/userfiles\/images\/langvan5.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u00ecn khung c\u1ea3nh \u1ea5y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00e1c linh h\u1ed3n n\u01a1i Luy\u1ec7n Ng\u1ee5c c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c an \u1ee7i nhi\u1ec1u. \u01af\u1edbc mong ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n tr\u1ebb \u00fd th\u1ee9c h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n s\u00e1m h\u1ed1i n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/phatdiem.org\/User_folder_upload\/userfiles\/images\/langvan8.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/phatdiem.org\/User_folder_upload\/userfiles\/images\/langvan2.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u201cT\u1eeb v\u1ef1c th\u1eb3m, con k\u00eau l\u00ean Ng\u00e0i, l\u1ea1y CH\u00daA, \u00a0mu\u00f4n l\u1ea1y Ch\u00faa, xin Ng\u00e0i nghe ti\u1ebfng con\u201d\u00a0(Tv 130,1-2) Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u0103m m\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 2019-\u00a0S\u00e1m h\u1ed1i &amp; N\u00ean th\u00e1nh, c\u00e1ch ri\u00eang trong th\u00e1ng 11-C\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c linh h\u1ed3n, l\u1eddi Th\u00e1nh v\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y th\u1eadt ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00e2m t\u00ecnh gi\u1edd c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n Taiz\u00e9 c\u1ee7a &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":424,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[14,9],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tintuc5.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/423"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tintuc5.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tintuc5.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tintuc5.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tintuc5.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=423"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/tintuc5.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/423\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":801,"href":"https:\/\/tintuc5.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/423\/revisions\/801"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"em